comments: Beasley (MIN) rests his forearm on Rozier's (CHA) front at the end of the drive and marginal contact occurs.
Rozier (CHA) makes the pass and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs with Towns (MIN) thereafter.
Biyombo (CHA) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Towns' (MIN) right arm after the release. Towns' reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Beasley (MIN) rests his hand on Rozier's (CHA) side and marginal contact occurs as Rozier dribbles inside the perimeter.
Beasley (MIN) moves forward as he contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Rozier's (CHA) front as Rozier returns to the floor.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path and absorbs the contact.
Biyombo (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in Beasley's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
Edwards (MIN) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball at the end of Rozier's (CHA) drive.
Beasley (MIN) extends his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Rozier's (CHA) side as he receives the pass.
Biyombo (CHA) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental contact with Bridges' (CHA) right arm as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Ball (CHA) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another after the shot is released.
McDaniels (MIN) makes incidental contact with Hayward's (CHA) right arm as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Rubio (MIN) commits a take foul on Ball (CHA).
McLaughlin (MIN) has his right hand on Ball's (CHA) right hip during the inbound and quickly removes it.
Rozier (CHA) and Beasley (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Beasley (MIN) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Towns (MIN) and Biyombo (CHA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Towns (MIN) and Hayward (CHA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Hayward (CHA) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Bridges (CHA).
Ball (CHA) and McLaughlin (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Beasley (MIN) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) rests his hand on Beasley's (MIN) left hip and marginal contact occurs as they move together toward the lane.
Towns (MIN) extends his hand forward and brushes Ball's (CHA) left arm as Ball loses control of the pass.
Edwards (MIN) has his arms around Graham's (CHA) upper half and marginal contact occurs as they move inside the perimeter together during the inbound.

Hayward (CHA) maintains verticality and absorbs the body contact made with Beasley (MIN) during the driving shot attempt. Hayward's left hand comes down after absorbing the initial contact and marginal contact occurs with Beasley's right arm during the follow-through.
Beasley (MIN) commits a take foul on Hayward (CHA).
